Hashtag island in the dustbin of history number one on Twitter .. And Twitter: No traitors and supporters of terrorism
02 Nov 2019, 11:58 by Sayed Ahmed
Mr. Ahmed after the launch of the media Ahmed Moussa Hashtag island in the dustbin of history, hashtag witnessed a large turnout of the masses and was able to occupy the first place on the social networking site "Twitter" The most prominent tweets are as follows: Al-Jazeera's Ally of Al-Jazeera is a despicable channel for its agents of the Zionists, ISIS and Muslim Brotherhood criminal criminals.This is the natural end of the dirtiest and most degraded media platform in the history of the whole Middle East. Lonely in the Arab and Islamic world supportive of terrorism because it is a treacherous agent channel contributed to the destruction of our country so we say that: # Aljazeera in the history of Al Jazeera Millions killed and displaced in the name of democracy
